Hello traveler, my name is Sean, I'm a member of the Explorers Society. I've spent years exploring the wonders of Dereth. There are many interesting corners of Dereth that sadly go unvisited, but that's why I'm here.

In order to introduce others to the joy of exploration I've placed markers on, above and below Dereth. If you feel the urge to explore you may come across a few of these Exploration Markers like the one next to me here. Come see me when you've found at least 10 of them and I'll reward you.
Go ahead and use this marker. I hope it will be the first of many you find while exploring the majesty of this world.

Over the past several months, I have been hiding more and more markers across this wondrous land. There are now a grand total of 100 markers hidden in the world, some of which are linked by theme. If you find all 100 markers, I may have something special for you.
